    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Cost: 2 Creation Points </p><p>Drain: 5 CCD Chakra </p><p></p><p>As an action you spend the CCD Drain of this enhancement to leap gracefully, shifting your rotational axis in a move that makes it seem as if you could ride on the moon itself.</p><p> Select a space within 30 feet to land with your trick.</p><p> All creatures who you would have passed through if you did not jump over them must make a Strength saving throw or take your A.Ts weapon damage + 2d6 and be knocked prone.</p><p></p>",
